Currently, in Confluence, the indicator for whether or not there are any attachments in a page is a paperclip icon on the top left corner of the page. 

However, this can be somewhat easily missed at times. Hence, it would be better if we had a better indicator of any attachments in the page; something that would clearly indicate at first glance of the page whether or not there are any attachments.

