"What I need is when replying to a previous comment by someone else to be able to start with a quoted copy of his/her text. Say someone said
{code}
I believe that's bug XYZ, right?
{code}
I want to hit a button "Reply quoted" or something that puts
{code}
{quote}
I believe that's bug XYZ, right?
{quote}
{code}
into the text field where I start typing my reply similar to what "Reply" does in Bugzilla and what [JRA-6412|https://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRA-6412] is asking for JIRA."

